parameters:
\N<Male> I never thought you would actually wear it and come
back.
\N<Male> I meant it as a light joke, you know.
It's hard to see from this angle.
\N<Hinata Aki> Do you have any idea how embarrassed I was?!

\N<Hinata Aki> I'm already being seen by people in town with
weird looks, treating me like a pervert!

\N<Hinata Aki> There were even people I know, and I almost
got caught!

\N<Omura> Well, it's fine since you didn't get caught,
right?
\N<Hinata Aki> ...Is it because it suits me?!

\N<Hinata Aki> I felt like someone was outside for a
moment... Maybe it was just my imagination?
